1. *James* se pohvalio svojim uspehom u školi. (James boasted about his success in school.)
2. Kada je *James* postao dečak, njegovi roditelji su bili ponosni na njega. (When James became a boy, his parents were proud of him.)
3. *James* je nedavno kupio novi automobil. (James recently bought a new car.)
4. Njegov otac i *James* su često išli u ribolov. (His father and James often went fishing.)
5. *James* je bio najbolji učenik u razredu. (James was the best student in the class.)